# Iter 1 — Backlog research + criteria

## Work Done
- Read CardPanel.tsx, BoardClient.tsx, schema.ts, agent-message/route.ts, cards.ts, move/route.ts
- Identified that agent work text is fetched from `/api/cards/:id/agent-message`
- Identified that the panel currently has NO split-panel UI; only a single scrollable content area
- Wrote research.md with file path references and design diagram
- Wrote criteria.md with 12 numbered acceptance criteria
- Wrote todo.md with 13 implementation steps
- Attached all three files and moved card to in-progress

## Key Findings
- `CardPanel.tsx:360` — the panel `div` uses `flex-col`; refactoring to split-panel is straightforward
- `CardPanel.tsx:404` — the content area is `flex-1 overflow-y-auto`; top panel stays the same, we add divider + bottom panel below
- Agent text API exists at `GET /api/cards/[id]/agent-message` returning `{ text: string | null }`
- localStorage key pattern: `card-panel-split-<cardId>` → stores bottom panel height in px

## Next
